Variable.name: eRate
Variable.equation: if(R < MinRadius ? MaxERate : if(R >= NCRadius ? InitialCrossSlope : (EFD - F)))
Variable.description: Calculated Cross Slope Value | AASHTO 2011 Equation 3-20

Variable.name: rPI
Variable.description: Radius at Point of Intersection | AASHTO 2011 Equation 3-11

Variable.name: hPI
Variable.description: Point of Intersection Offset from 1/R Axis | AASHTO 2011 Equation 3-12

Variable.name: MO
Variable.description: Middle Ordinate of f Distribution Curve | AASHTO 2011 Equation 3-16

Variable.name: NCRadius
Variable.description: Normal Crown Radius Based on Design Speed | AASHTO 2011 Table 3-10a

Variable.name: frictionFactor
Variable.description: Max Side Friction Factor Based on Design Speed | AASHTO 2011 Table 3-7

Variable.name: runningSpeed
Variable.description: Running Speed Based on Design Speed | AASHTO 2011 Table 3-6

Variable.name: bw
Variable.description: Adjustment Factor for Number of Lanes Rotated | Derived from AASHTO 2011 Table 3-16

Table.description: Maximum Relative Gradient Based on Design Speed

CustomKeyStations.description: Adjustment for Inside, Outside, Right, or Left pivot
CustomKeyStations.criteria: (PivotType = 1 OR PivotType = 2 OR PivotType = 3 OR PivotType = 4) AND NRotatedLanes =2

Variable.name: RunoutDistance
Variable.equation: ComputedTransitionLength * ( abs( InitialCrossSlope) /((2 * MaxE) - abs( InitialCrossSlope)))
